      "message": "Seems like just the terminology they use for if you provide values directly using glVertexAttrib. The enum to get them is called GL_CURRENT_VERTEX_ATTRIB. In the GLES2 spec, section 2.7, it says \"Current generic attribute values define generic attributes for a vertex when a vertex array defining that data is not enabled\"",
